* Coefficient tables

The table tables/field_gg_coef_table.jl is created from src/create_field_gg_coef_table.jl
The table tables/field_monomial_functions.jl is created from src/field_monomial_functions.jl

These tables are used by various programs. These tables do not have to be recreated unless
you want to extend the derivative range. Currently derivatives up to order 12 are tabulated.

